{"tid":1389151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日義士東區法院提堂, 請大家入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-30T23:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:56:53.000Z","uid":113038,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1e50422169272909836e28c85d266ebb300bca25","tid":1389151,"uid":113038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:42:23.000Z","msg":"見出面好多Post既人都有誤解, 訓唔著簡介補充返小小野比大家<br />\n<br />\n被控暴動罪既義士今日只係提堂 (Mention), 即日唔會審訊 (Trial), 更加唔會判刑 (Sentence). 今日只係走程序<br />\n<br />\n新案件Fresh Cases通常會係第一庭 (6/F) <strong>9:30</strong> 提堂 (第一庭大把案過堂, 未必開庭就即刻到義士), 地下門口會貼審訊案件表. 通常會遲少少開庭 (睇法官心情), 開庭之前義士應該會係7樓當值律師服務辦事處搵當值律師幫手<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今日會發生既事:</strong><br />\n提堂黎講, 法庭書記會宣讀控罪, 法庭聽取答辯(Take Plea), 被告要回答認罪/唔認罪. 如果認罪，法庭聽取求情陳詞後就會考慮判刑, 如果唔認罪法官會將案件審訊排期移交至區域法院，之後批埋保釋同保釋條件, 被告去會計部交保釋金 (如果批保釋), 走得. (唔批就即時還押, unlikely)<br />\n<br />\n就算第一庭都好細, 一定入唔晒 (平時都爆), 會去支持既人入到既請<strong>記得熄電話, 保持安靜</strong>, 唔好叫口號, 庭出面都唔好亂黎, 一陣拉埋告你藐視法庭就hihi, 出法院就如常啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外, <strong>區域法院唔會有陪審團</strong>, 所以好可惜另外一個Post講陪審團否決權 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386844/page/1</a>) 係<strong>不成立</strong>, 而點解去區域法院,  點解冇陪審團, 請追一追另一位巴打呢個Post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387520/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387520/page/1</a>), <strong>亦請大家睇下入面既判詞, 你會為發現法庭同普通人對法律/正義既見解係好大出入</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇完你可能覺得法例on9, 暴動咁易入?? 咁既法治狗也不屌<br />\n其實香港法官/司法系統已經算公道<br />\n唔公義係在於<strong>執法</strong>同<strong>立法 </strong>, 亦正正係訴求既重點<br />\n<br />\n希望義士能免除刑責 多謝你地既付出<br />\n大家加油 香港加油"},{"pid":"2d310141e1d990f3d5008686c88cabe92f839899","tid":1389151,"uid":256561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:44:45.000Z","msg":"多謝提供資訊，持續跟進事件，絕不放棄手足！"},{"pid":"0166f260828d62448a503cd4458312daca5a6769","tid":1389151,"uid":113038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b3b48ab15e3004a95ff479b91a505223aef437","tid":1389151,"uid":202129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6f8746562ecc1beba4e883659431bf494bcc497","tid":1389151,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:02:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊，會唔會留席俾親人朋友先好d"},{"pid":"bc2f24f7472632280847efa5d9d4d89f7c832a14","tid":1389151,"uid":113038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6f8746562ecc1beba4e883659431bf494bcc497","tid":1389151,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:02:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊，會唔會留席俾親人朋友先好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:07:29.000Z","msg":"庭入面有記者, 咁多單Case既控辯, 被告, 其他人, 一次告咁多個基本上個庭爆硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 庭出面都會好多人"},{"pid":"07975db1430d4f74bf08036e0c1b6911b75c5459","tid":1389151,"uid":3782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"去緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319005fb9571552b62f69bb815326cf915815346","tid":1389151,"uid":201853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"291cdf6dd59962bd74e84f72c04d642fd58e63be","tid":1389151,"uid":292566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"如果係羅德泉，保釋機會很大"},{"pid":"7f15f367df53c1af578442fcff5f0da628746dc2","tid":1389151,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNoQmxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h